    <a href="/reading/algorithms/" class="text-sm mb-4 inline-block">&larr; back to algorithms</a>

    <h1>Graphs</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Nievergelt &amp; Hinrichs &middot; Ch. 6 &middot; <a href="https://textbookequity.org/algorithms-and-data-structures/">Algorithms and Data Structures</a></p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">A <strong>graph</strong> is vertices and edges. Represent it as an adjacency list (sparse) or adjacency matrix (dense). <strong>BFS</strong> explores level by level. <strong>DFS</strong> explores depth-first. Both run in O(V + E).</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SVG: Graph with BFS frontier highlighted -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-6">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" class="w-full max-w-md" style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;">
        <!-- Edges -->
        <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="100" y2="100" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="300" y2="100" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="100" y1="100" x2="60" y2="180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="100" y1="100" x2="160" y2="180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="300" y1="100" x2="260" y2="180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="300" y1="100" x2="350" y2="180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="160" y1="180" x2="260" y2="180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.3"/>
        <!-- BFS frontier rings -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="22" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
        <circle cx="200" cy="120" r="110" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3" stroke-opacity="0.2"/>
        <!-- Nodes -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="16" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" stroke-opacity="0.7"/>
        <text x="200" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="12">A</text>
        <text x="200" y="18" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="9">d=0</text>

        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="16" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="2" stroke-opacity="0.7"/>
        <text x="100" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="#34d399" font-size="12">B</text>
        <text x="75" y="92" fill="#34d399" font-size="9">d=1</text>

        <circle cx="300" cy="100" r="16" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="2" stroke-opacity="0.7"/>
        <text x="300" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="#34d399" font-size="12">C</text>
        <text x="325" y="92" fill="#34d399" font-size="9">d=1</text>

        <circle cx="60" cy="180" r="16" fill="none" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="2" stroke-opacity="0.7"/>
